Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像下雪一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.68,0:00:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的櫻花就快謝了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.14,0:00:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 明天休息大家來賞花吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠻有趣的 我來做便當吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.52,0:00:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.24,0:00:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我也會做的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.30,0:01:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊 我就隨便決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.02,0:01:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里 我這邊不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我帶點什麼去好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.46,0:01:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.73,0:01:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來 弘樹總是給你們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.80,0:01:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 多不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘樹  璘兒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天八點在公園集合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.40,0:01:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那九點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.78,0:01:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賞花都是午飯後開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.39,0:01:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒? 那十點...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我還想看超星神Gransazer呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}超星神Gransazer:2003年在TV東京播出10月年番，共計51話.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.54,0:01:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還是中午吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.62,0:02:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.08,0:02:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉 水桶放在哪里來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 在水池下麵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.57,0:02:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.01,0:02:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天可能會下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是要刮南風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}南風: 劇中是「春の嵐」意思是日本每年春季刮來的較強勁南風 通常會伴隨著暴雨和龍捲風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南風...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已經下起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.30,0:02:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 下得還真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.64,0:02:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做個晴天娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.71,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧做了晴天娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.27,0:03:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下不會都被打落了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青草的芳香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花都沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.11,0:03:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弘樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.76,0:04:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漫天佈滿花瓣啊



